320
00:22:14,390 --> 00:22:19,230
Ryou-omoi (両思い) is the opposite of Kata-omoi (片思い, means unrequited
love), which indicates that she was wishing to be his teacher's girlfriend.

321
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:20,680
