she shouldn't fall in love with.

322
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:42,210
You may not believe me, but..

323
00:22:42,210 --> 00:22:44,690
..that's the truth.

324
00:22:44,690 --> 00:22:46,710
I see.

325
00:22:46,710 --> 00:22:52,200
So, that's what happened around 8pm.

326
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:56,790
