- Ah, it's nothing..

327
00:22:56,790 --> 00:22:59,600
On the contrary, I checked
on things unrelated to me.

328
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:01,190
No, it's okay.

329
00:23:01,190 --> 00:23:04,710
Each night, my heart beats faster around 8pm.

330
