337
00:23:52,190 --> 00:23:54,180
No one knows..

338
00:23:54,180 --> 00:23:58,200
..about Yano-sensei before
he came to teach in this school.

339
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:03,770
I think, I tend to intervene
with somebody else's problem.

340
00:24:03,770 --> 00:24:07,680
Make sure you remember things
you have to do before 3pm!

341
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:11,200
