342
00:24:12,710 --> 00:24:19,180
If you really want to go to public university,
you have to be more focused on your study.

343
00:24:21,210 --> 00:24:26,180
Sensei, did you ever fall
in love with your student?

344
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:31,180
Why do you ask suddenly? I never did.
