345
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:36,690
But there was a student who liked you, right?

346
00:24:36,690 --> 00:24:38,690
So, what?

347
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:46,200
What are you thinking about that girl?

348
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:49,700
