351
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:07,180
If it's just a misunderstanding..

352
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:09,200
There was.

353
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:11,700
..I think.

354
00:25:13,190 --> 00:25:16,690
It's not a misunderstanding!

355
00:25:16,690 --> 00:25:20,700
At the end, I don't know what it was
 and I can never find out what it was.

356
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:23,200
Don't spead any weird gossip, okay?

357
00:25:31,710 --> 00:25:35,700
She was died before she could
convey her true feeling. It's tragic..

358
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:38,180
So tragic!

359
00:25:38,180 --> 00:25:41,190
Because no one knows
when they will die, right?

360
00:25:41,190 --> 00:25:44,190
Moreover, her feeling has been
considered as a misunderstanding.

361
00:25:44,190 --> 00:25:48,780
I'm so vexed!
- Why are you so vexed?

362
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:52,200
Although it felt so painful,
she kept holding back her feeling.

363
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:57,200
Then suddenly, everything had come to its end.
You don't know how frustrating it feels!

364
00:25:57,200 --> 00:26:01,190
I know that feeling!

365
00:26:01,190 --> 00:26:07,730
You're talking about how it felt when your
waist hurt and you have to leave the boat club.

366
00:26:07,730 --> 00:26:11,700
Both your efforts and dreams became nothing.

367
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:14,700
Nothing at all.

368
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:23,180
That girl's love is also considered as nothing.

369
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:26,210
Although it really did exist.

370
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:28,770
Mihane..

371
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:31,700
Although you can leap through time..

372
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:35,690
You are not allowed to
change that girl's fate, okay?

373
00:26:35,690 --> 00:26:40,690
Or else, you would snatch out Nishioka-kun's life.

374
00:26:44,700 --> 00:26:46,730
I understand.

375
00:26:57,210 --> 00:27:01,200
Anyway, Goro..
- Hm?

376
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:05,700
You like Mihane, right?

377
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,960
Eh?!

378
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:14,800
Actually, I think I'm also
falling in love with Mihane.

379
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:19,700
I wonder if it's alright for two
people, to love the same person.

380
00:27:19,700 --> 00:27:22,200
What's with that question?

381
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:26,190
This is my first love,
so I don't really get it.

382
00:27:26,190 --> 00:27:30,690
If it's alright, then we're good.

383
00:27:30,690 --> 00:27:33,210
For the rest..

384
00:27:33,210 --> 00:27:37,210
We should just leave it to Mihane.

385
00:27:39,170 --> 00:27:41,190
Let her decide, right?

386
00:27:41,190 --> 00:27:43,690
See ya!

387
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:52,200
Goro..

388
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,720
Have you ever kissed?

389
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:58,290
Huh?!

390
00:27:58,290 --> 00:28:02,690
I wonder if Mihane has ever kissed.

391
00:28:02,690 --> 00:28:05,700
I don't know!

392
00:28:05,700 --> 00:28:08,180
So, it means..

393
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:11,700
Gora and Mihane..

394
00:28:11,700 --> 00:28:15,170
..have never kissed yet.

395
00:28:15,170 --> 00:28:17,220
Yosh!

396
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:19,260
Yosh~
- Yosh?

397
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:21,180
Yosh! Yosh! Yosh!

398
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:24,680
What the heck does he mean?!

399
00:28:30,990 --> 00:28:32,960
Bye~ Bye~ Bee~

400
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,960
Bye~ Bye~ Bee~

401
00:28:41,890 --> 00:28:44,370
I don't say anything!
Please don't eat my brain!

402
00:28:44,370 --> 00:28:46,420
I won't eat your brain.

403
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,420
In exchange for that..

404
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:54,360
Please give me some food!

405
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:59,370
I'm back!
- Welcome back!

406
00:28:59,370 --> 00:29:01,870
Mii-kun..
- Hm?

407
00:29:01,870 --> 00:29:04,390
I have a friend who looks hungry.

408
00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:07,390
May I give her a Buta-tama?

409
00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:07,390
Buta-tama (ぶたたま, Pork Omelet) is a an Okonomiyaki (お好み焼き) a Japanese
savoury pancake containing a variety of ingredients) with some pork-toppings.

410
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:12,880
For your friend?
Of course, you may.

411
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:15,380
Why don't you invite her to come here?

412
00:29:16,870 --> 00:29:20,370
Don't you have a house or a family?

413
00:29:20,370 --> 00:29:24,880
They are so far,
and I can't go home.

414
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:28,930
But you have a friend, right?
- Oh, you're talking about Senpai?

415
00:29:28,930 --> 00:29:30,970
He pisses me off!

416
00:29:30,970 --> 00:29:33,970
You have a fight?
- Something like that.

417
00:29:36,370 --> 00:29:41,370
What do you call this?
Buta-tama? This is the best!

418
00:29:44,380 --> 00:29:49,870
Because Mii-kun made it!
- Mii-kun? Who is that?

419
00:29:49,870 --> 00:29:53,370
He is not my real dad,
but he is my dad.

420
00:29:58,010 --> 00:30:00,510
I see.

421
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:03,370
Here comes the weakness!

422
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:06,890
This is impossible, right?!

423
00:30:06,890 --> 00:30:08,800
"Chapter 7"

424
00:30:09,700 --> 00:30:13,430
"With a kiss, make her fall (in love)!"

425
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:17,380
This sounds bad, really!

426
00:30:17,380 --> 00:30:19,880
Welcome home!
- Ah, I'm home..

427
00:30:24,370 --> 00:30:26,370
Here it is.

428
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:32,410
Taco-rice!

429
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:32,410
