441
00:31:34,870 --> 00:31:39,410
"I wonder if it's alright for two
people, to love the same person."

442
00:31:39,410 --> 00:31:42,980
It's not alright!

443
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:45,370
Heck~

444
00:31:45,370 --> 00:31:49,390
I bring some university
