00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:16,370
Eh? Then, I'll hang up first.

452
00:32:16,370 --> 00:32:19,370
Let me countdown, ready?

453
00:32:19,370 --> 00:32:22,370
1.. 2..

454
00:32:22,370 --> 00:32:24,890
Why don't you hang up?
You break the rule..

455
00:32:24,890 --> 00:32:26,320
This time, I'll hang up.

456
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:27,440
Here I go.

457
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:29,860
1.. 2..

458
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:33,380
What the hell are you doing?!
- Who is that Jun-kun?

459
00:32:33,380 --> 00:32:36,890
My boyfriend.
- Eh, you have a boyfriend?

460
00:32:36,890 --> 00:32:41,390
Of course, I have.
I'm already an eight-grader!

461
00:32:36,890 --> 00:32:41,390
