491
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:36,890
What kind of moments do you
want to keep forever, Mihane?

492
00:34:36,890 --> 00:34:39,390
I want to to see those moments.

493
00:34:42,900 --> 00:34:45,450
Sorry for being so inconsiderate.

494
00:34:45,450 --> 00:34:48,380
It's okay.

495
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:52,890
